58.6	Montpellier	Montpellier	Montpellier (French pronunciation: ; Occitan: Montpelhièr; Catalan: ) is a city in southern France. It is the capital of the Languedoc-Roussillon region, as well as the Hérault department. Montpellier is the 8th largest city of the country, and is also the fastest growing city in France over the past 25 years.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ea/Montpellier_fg02.jpg/270px-Montpellier_fg02.jpg
